  "prompt": "I deleted my friend ID from WeChat. How do I find it again?",
  "response": "If you've deleted your friend's ID from WeChat, you won't be able to retrieve it directly through the app since the contact has been removed from your account. However, you can try the following methods to reconnect with your friend:\n\n### 1. Search Using Other Information:\n- **Search by Username or Phone Number:** If you remember your friend's username or phone number that is linked to their WeChat account, you can use the search function in the app to find them.\n- **Search in Groups:** If you and your friend were part of any mutual groups on WeChat, you can find their contact information in the group member list.\n- **Check Chat History:** If you had any chat history with your friend before deleting the contact, you might be able to see their profile picture and username in the chat list, even though their contact is deleted. This might give you clues to search for them again.\n\n### 2. Ask Mutual Friends:\n- **Reach Out to Mutual Friends:** If you have any mutual friends on WeChat, ask them to share your friend's contact information with you.\n\n### 3. Other Communication Methods:\n- **Other Social Media Accounts:** Contact your friend via other social media platforms like Facebook, WhatsApp, or Instagram, and ask them to share their WeChat ID.\n\n### 4. Search By Moments or Comments:\n- **Check Moments Comments:** If your friend has commented on your moments (posts on WeChat), you might be able to find their profile and add them back from the comments section.\n\n### 5. WeChat Contact Backup:\n- **Backup and Restore Contacts:** If you have performed a backup of your WeChat contacts, you can restore it to recover deleted contacts.\n\n### 6. Official Account:\n- **Customer Service:** Contact WeChat customer service for assistance. They might help you recover deleted IDs if possible.\n\n### Additional Tips:\n- **Save or Export Contacts Regularly:** To avoid losing contacts in the future, consider saving or exporting your contacts periodically.\n\nUltimately, the most straightforward approach is to reach out to mutual friends or use other forms of communication to get your friend's WeChat ID.",
